Package: XML2R
Title: EasieR XML data collection
Version: 0.0.6
Author: Carson Sievert <sievert@iastate.edu>
Maintainer: Carson Sievert <sievert@iastate.edu>
Description: XML2R is a framework that reduces the effort required to
